            <arrangement id="aspace_c95311d3d727e5c75735efcdbfd29909">
               <head>Arrangement</head>
               <p>The addition to the Cornelius Osgood papers is arranged alphabetically by location.</p>
            </arrangement>
            <scopecontent id="aspace_8508fe1720fb6199a9f29992cc447e62">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The addition consists of photographs taken by Cornelius Osgood during his career as an ethnologist from 1927 to 1966.  The photographs document the lives of people, commercial and agricultural enterprises, street scenes, archaelogical excavations, and cultural events in Asia, the Americas and the Caribbean.</p>
            </scopecontent>
